      <div class="content-prose">
        
        <div class="work-grid">
          <div class="work-card">
            <h3><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> How to Submit</h3>
            <p>Start through WhatsApp. Send clear photos or PDFs. We review promptly and provide accurate quotes based on actual content.</p>
            <p>For confidential matters: encrypted email or client portals available.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="work-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-check-double"></i> Quality & Accuracy</h3>
            <p>No guesswork in legal translation. When source text is ambiguous, we note it. If originals contain errors, we flag them—we don't "correct" them.</p>
            <p>Every translation passes quality checks for terminology, completeness, and formatting.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="work-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Confidentiality</h3>
            <p>Strict confidentiality for all documents. Translators work under confidentiality obligations. No sharing with third parties.</p>
            <p>Enhanced security protocols available for sensitive matters.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="work-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Getting Started</h3>
            <p>Send documents through WhatsApp for quick review and quote. Whether you face a court deadline tomorrow or plan ahead, we advise on appropriate service level.</p>
            <p>Law firms: ask about volume pricing and dedicated contacts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <InlineCallout 
        type="tip" 
        title="Need Attestation?"
        link="/services/attestation/"
        linkText="View attestation services"
      >
